data.description: ***NEW VINYL SIDING WILL BE INSTALLED FOR BUYER!!!***Wonderful starter home nestled on a spacious corner lot! Large laundry room has a closet and could be converted into THIRD bedroom, if buyer desires to move the washer and dryer downstairs! This absolute cutie has had a new roof installed in 2021, sewer line was replaced by previous owners from home to street, updated flooring & a basement that is great for storage! The spacious backyard is fully fenced with a sweet 12x16 workshop with power, & storage sheds, as well as room for RV parking!
